N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5705.1 - Compliance with orders of authority employees or police

State Regulations

No person using the facilities shall fail, neglect or refuse
to comply with any lawful order of any authority employee or police
officer. Notes
